    <item>
      <title>新加坡元因政策前景而升至十年高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/singapore-dollar-trades-around-ten-year-high-on-policy-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员权衡新加坡货币当局相对强硬的政策前景与美联储的政策前景之间的差异，新加坡元升至近十年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/singapore-dollar-trades-around-ten-year-high-on-policy-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 23:18:45 GMT</pubDate>
